FAQ
Common questions
Is WeedStop really free?
Yes, 100% free forever. No subscriptions, no hidden costs, no credit card required.
Is my data private?
Fully anonymous â€” no real name, no email verification, no data selling. Your journey stays private.
When is the full release?
WeedStop is currently in beta. The full Android release is coming soon. iOS is planned for the future.
Can it replace professional treatment?
No. WeedStop is a supportive tool that complements professional help. If you're struggling with severe addiction, please consult a healthcare professional.
How do leaderboards work?
5 mini-games currently feature global leaderboards. Your highscores are ranked against all users worldwide, completely anonymously.
